OL,3,CJersey government criticised for
OL,4,C#111.8m spend on consultants
OL,6,FThe Jersey government is facing
OL,7,Fcriticism for being "too reliant" on
OL,8,Fconsultants after a massive #111.8m
OL,9,Fspend, according to a review of their
OL,10,Fcurrent role in .
OL,12,FThe report by Jersey's Comptroller and
OL,13,FAuditor General was a follow-up into
OL,14,Fhow consultants were used on the
OL,15,Fisland and found the practice was "not
OL,16,Fvalue for money".
