OL,3,CJersey government criticised for
OL,4,C#111.8m spend on consultants
OL,6,FAnother example saw the government
OL,7,Fspend more than #300,000 annually on
OL,8,Fjust one consultant.
OL,10,FThe Auditor General Lynn Pamment CBE
OL,11,Fstated: "Some of the contractors being
OL,12,Fused by Government are ex-employees
OL,13,Fpaid at higher rates than when they
OL,14,Fwere employees."
OL,16,FShe has called for an overarching
OL,17,Fworkforce plan to be implemented to
OL,18,Fmove away from consultants.
