OL,3,CJersey government criticised for
OL,4,C#111.8m spend on consultants
OL,6,FDespite this, the Chief Minister also
OL,7,Fsaid that the use of consultants can
OL,8,Fbe "justifiable".
OL,10,FHe explained: "We have to bring in
OL,11,Fcertain skills for major projects and
OL,12,Fwe cannot avoid that because we don't
OL,13,Fhave the skills on the island to deal
OL,14,Fwith things like that.
OL,16,F"So there are exceptions to the rule."
